   Korea to seek her only remaining relatives. Once she reaches Korea,

   marriage. Having nothing more than a picture of Kang Jae, Failan spends 
   her days dreaming and wishing that Kang Jae would come to visit her.

   thinks about him, but never has the nerve to give the letters to Kang
